data.description: Welcome to 315 Lone Tree Dr, your new home! This stunning house boasts three bedrooms, and two and a half bathrooms, and is fully move-in ready. The main floor features an inviting family room with a cozy fireplace, while the open kitchen and dining area are perfect for hosting family and friends. You'll love the new appliances and island, as well as the convenient access to the oversized 2-car garage. Upstairs, you'll find the primary bedroom with a beautiful tray ceiling and en-suite private bath, along with two additional bedrooms and a bonus room. The ideally located laundry makes household chores a breeze. The backyard is a serene retreat, with a deck that's perfect for unwinding in the evenings. This home is located within the award-winning Clover school district and won't last long. Don't miss out on the chance to make this your new home!
